tll-http (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * doc: Describe prefix paths for uws
  * http: Install http control scheme
  * lws: Return UNKNOWN for unknown enum values
  * uwsc:
    Clear client pointer on close
    Export local and remote address
    Fix invalid logger pointer conversion
    Report ping-pong RTT
    Use local libuwsc fork

 -- Pavel Shramov <shramov@mexmat.net>  Sat, 01 Nov 2025 10:55:43 +0300

